{
  "info": {
    "name": "Swag Labs API Test Suite",
    "description": "Swag Labs 电商平台 + JSONPlaceholder RESTful API 接口测试套件\n被测接口: Swag Labs (7) + JSONPlaceholder (10) = 17\n创建: 2026.06.22 | 作者: 贾杰超\n\n⚠️ Swag Labs 是 React SPA，返回空壳 HTML，仅验证 HTTP 200。\nJSONPlaceholder 是免费的假数据 REST API，支持 GET/POST/PUT/PATCH/DELETE。\n原计划 ReqRes 于 2025 年改版需 API Key，改用 JSONPlaceholder 替代。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url_swag",   "value": "https://www.saucedemo.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "base_url_json",   "value": "https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "created_post_ids","value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
